Package it.unipr.zezacracolici

Class Person

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.zezacracolici.Person
Direct Known Subclasses:
Member, Staff
public class Person extends Object
The class Person is in charge of saving a person object with its properties. Each person has an username, password, name, surname, fiscalcode and address.
Since:
1.0
Version:
